@description.body:
Map action to combination of method and URL pattern.

<pre class="javascript">
res.map("get", "GET", "/photos/{id}", {id: /\d+/});

// GET /photos/123
res.get({id: "123"});
</pre>

Abort action.

Example:

<pre class="javascript">
// Abort all invocations of action
res.get({id: 1});
res.get({id: 2});
res.abort("get");

// Abort specific invocation of action (by id)
var actionId = res.get({id: 1});
res.abort(actionId);
</pre>
